         <t:abstract>
            <t:p>
               This is the short recension of the hagiography. In all likelihood older than <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7152GadlaYo">Gadla ʾAbbā Yoḥanni za-Dabra ʿAśā</t:ref>, it is also much more widespread.
               It was edited and translated in <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/7QSFGIDF"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Basset1884ViedAbba"/><title level="a">Vie d’Abbā Yohanni. Texte éthiopien, traduction française avec une introduction</title><title level="j">Bulletin de correspondance africaine</title><author><forename>René</forename><surname>Basset</surname></author><date>1884</date><biblScope unit="volume">3</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">433-453</biblScope><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Hagiography</note><note type="tag">bm:Basset1884ViedAbba</note><note type="tag">Yohanni</note></note><note type="tag">Hagiography</note><note type="tag">bm:Basset1884ViedAbba</note><note type="tag">Yohanni</note></t:bibl>.
            </t:p>
         </t:abstract>
