         <t:div type="edition">
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="prologue" xml:lang="gez">
               <t:note>The following prologue is taken from <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/7QSFGIDF"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Basset1884ViedAbba"/><title level="a">Vie d’Abbā Yohanni. Texte éthiopien, traduction française avec une introduction</title><title level="j">Bulletin de correspondance africaine</title><author><forename>René</forename><surname>Basset</surname></author><date>1884</date><biblScope unit="volume">3</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">433-453</biblScope><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Hagiography</note><note type="tag">bm:Basset1884ViedAbba</note><note type="tag">Yohanni</note></note><note type="tag">Hagiography</note><note type="tag">bm:Basset1884ViedAbba</note><note type="tag">Yohanni</note></t:bibl>.</t:note>
               <t:ab>
                  በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ሥሉስ፡ ኅቡር፡ እላዌሁ፡ ልዑል፡ ዘኢይረክብዎ፡ ክቡት፡ ዘኢይሬእይዎ፡ እሳት፡ ዘኢይለክፍዎ፡
                  መንፈስ፡ ዘኢይገሥሥዎ፡ ኀይል፡ ዘኢይሌብውዎ፡ ንጉሥ፡ ዘኢይሰይምዎ፡ አምላክነ፡ በመ<t:supplied reason="omitted">ለ</t:supplied>ኮቱ፡ ወአቡነ፡ በኂሩቱ፡
                  ወአሐደ፡ ይጼልዩ፡ ወአሐደ፡ ይሰግድ፡ ወአሐደ፡ ይሴብሑ፡ ሎቱ፡ ስብሐት፡ እስከ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።
                  ንጽሕፍ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ገድሉ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ወብፁዕ፡ አባ፡ ዮሐኒ፡ እስመ፡ ውእቱ፡ ኮከብ፡ ብሩህ፡ ዘብሔረ፡ አግዓዚ፡
                  ወገባሬ፡ ተአምር፡ ዘደብረ፡ ዓሣ፡ ጸሎቱ፡ ወበረከቱ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስሌነ፡ አሜን።
               </t:ab>
            </t:div>
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
               <t:note>The following incipit is taken from <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/7QSFGIDF"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Basset1884ViedAbba"/><title level="a">Vie d’Abbā Yohanni. Texte éthiopien, traduction française avec une introduction</title><title level="j">Bulletin de correspondance africaine</title><author><forename>René</forename><surname>Basset</surname></author><date>1884</date><biblScope unit="volume">3</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">433-453</biblScope><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Hagiography</note><note type="tag">bm:Basset1884ViedAbba</note><note type="tag">Yohanni</note></note><note type="tag">Hagiography</note><note type="tag">bm:Basset1884ViedAbba</note><note type="tag">Yohanni</note></t:bibl>.</t:note>
               <t:ab>
                  ስምዑ፡ አኀውየ፡ ዜና፡ ገድሉ፡ ለብእሴ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ቅዱስ፡ ወብፁዕ፡ አባ፡ ዮሐኒ። ወሀሎ፡ ፩ብእሲ፡ ሥዩመ፡ 
                  ተምቤን፡ እስመ፡ ዓቢይ፡ ወክቡር፡ ውእቱ፡ እምነ፡ ሥዩማን፡ ዘይእቲ፡ ሀገር፡ ወጽኑዕ፡ ፈድፋደ፡ እምነ፡ ኵሉ፡ 
                  ወሖረ፡ ውስተ፡ ጽብዕ፡ ምስለ፡ ብዙኅ፡ ጸባኢት፡ ኀበ፡ ብሔረ፡ ኖባ፡ ወሶባ፡    
               </t:ab>
            </t:div>
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="explicit" xml:lang="gez">
               <t:ab>
                  ስብሐት፡ ለአብ፡ ለዘኃረዮ፡ እምከርሠ፡ እሙ፡ ወሰጊድ፡ <t:choice><t:sic>ለውልድ፡</t:sic><t:corr resp="MV">ለወልድ፡</t:corr></t:choice> 
                  በዘጸገዎ፡ ንጽሐ፡ ከመ፡ መላእክት፡ አኰቴት፡ ለመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ለዘወሀቦ፡ ወሐብአ፡ እምገጸ፡ ሞት። ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፡
               </t:ab>
            </t:div>
         </t:div>
      </t:body>
   </t:text></TEI>